window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Bono met his wife in high school, Park says.</p> <p>So did Jerry Lee Lewis, Eleanor answers.</p> <p>I’m not kidding, he says.</p> <p>You should be, she says, we’re 16.</p> <p>What about Romeo and Juliet?</p> <p>Shallow, confused, then dead.</p> <p>I love you, Park says.</p> <p>Wherefore art thou, Eleanor answers.</p> <p>I’m not kidding, he says.</p> <p>You should be.</p> <p>Set over the course of one school year in 1986, this is the story of two star-crossed misfits - smart enough to know that first love almost never lasts, but brave and desperate enough to try. When Eleanor meets Park, you’ll remember your own first love - and just how hard it pulled you under.</p>"; 
